PrecisWAYS AND MEANS MOTION REMISSION ORDER, 1995 which remits customs duties on certains goods that have become subject to duty as a result of statutory amendments proposed in a Notice of Ways and Means Motion tabled in the House on June 13, 1995 and restores the duty-free treatment previously accorded these goods.
